  "title": "Lorry Crane Driver #79392",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building and Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Lorry Crane Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide (Office at Tuas)</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (8.00am – 5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic up to $3000 + OT + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive a lorry and operate a lorry crane to transport materials and perform safe lifting at sites.</li><li>Follow Singapore traffic laws and all plant/site safety rules.</li><li>Plan routes and schedules to ensure on‑time deliveries, including diesel dispensing.</li><li>Load and unload using proper tools; secure cargo safely.</li><li>Do daily vehicle/crane checks, clean the vehicle, and report defects immediately.</li><li>Keep accurate logs (mileage, fuel, deliveries).</li><li>Fetch workers to and from construction sites when needed.</li><li>Other tasks as assigned by Management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Singapore Class 4 or Class 5 driving licence.</li><li>WSQ Lorry Crane Operation certificate (or equivalent).</li><li>At least 2 years’ driving experience in Singapore and 1 year operating a lorry crane.</li><li>Basic vehicle maintenance knowledge.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79392 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
